    <h1>Professional</h1>

    <p class="prose" style="margin-bottom: 2rem;">Data Scientist with 10 years of work experience, including 7 years in academia and 3 years in industry. I am passionate about helping people extract valuable insights from data and seek projects where I can both contribute and continue learning. I enjoy collaborating with colleagues and developing innovative solutions. I have experience in deploying machine learning models, deploying web based interactive visualizations, and extracting insights from data.</p>

